Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.40,0:00:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离地球4亿英里 存在这一个迷你太阳系 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Four hundred million miles from Earth, exists a mini solar system
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,60多个卫星围绕着一个强大的气态行星旋转 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of over 60 moons rotating around a powerful planet of gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.77,0:00:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它流动的颜色和斑点保持了奇异的美景 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Its flowing colors and spots hold strange beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.53,0:00:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而也包含了强烈的风暴 喷射气流 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but contain violent storms and jet streams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个巨大明亮的大气球会是伯利恒之星吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Could this big, bright ball of weather have been the Star of Bethlehem?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的其中的一个卫星会有生命生存在冰盖下吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Could one of its moons harbor life beneath its icy crust?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为生命分枝会存在在木卫二上 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We expect that branches of life would exist on Europa,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为水是其主要特征 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}just simply because water is the key feature.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去木卫二冰下垂钓 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I wanna go ice-fishing on Europa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打个洞潜入水中 看看四周  看到如果有什么…\NCut a hole, put a submersible, look around, see if anything…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么朝照相机游过来 拍打照相机 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}if anything swims up to the camera and licks the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我想做的 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}That's what I wanna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.03,0:00:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们地球要感激这个庞大的滑稽的磁体吗？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And does our own planet owe its survival to this massive comic magnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木星--巨大的行星 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Jupiter, the giant planet.
